            <lg xml:id="TK104">
<l>tiṉaittuṇai naṉṟi ceyiṉum paṉaittuṇaiyāk</l>
<l>koḷvar payaṉṟeri vār</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Even if one do a favor small as a millet grain, they who know the fruit</l>
<l>will deem it great as a palmyra tree.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
